user_description: Common sense advocate. My blog aims to focus on social challenges and potential solutions. Please visit, read and comment!
text: @AdzStats I don't think the #CovidVaccine will kill everyone. Risk remains rare, however in the young, the risk from vaccination is about equal to risk from #Covid_19 so mass vaccination is unethical and unjustified. Mass vaccination is entirely appropriate when disease risk is uniform
